name: DJ E-sus
description: Another blasphemous drop, DJ E-sus smashing the dancefloor with his killer beats. The visuals on the backdrop are extracted from a video I produced for one of my old songs. Also the sound is part of a track I produced.  An E-sus chord flows all along the track: how could it be otherwise? The main image comes from a photo I took to the "Santissimo Crocifisso" Church's portal, in Castegneto Carducci (Tuscany, Italy) Take this lysergic glitchy holy madness.
